{"tid":1861572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位醫護界同事，讓我地一齊見證歷史！罷工救港","createTime":"2020-02-04T07:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:22:35.000Z","uid":147696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c87da5467deb1ab130612aa7b57eeb9f300f8d56","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"醫管局員工陣線既手足有成2萬人，當日投票超過99%人投讚成罷工，點解今日只係得9000人簽左投名狀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你覺得<br />\n9000人力量定係20000人力量大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要秋後既9000人易定20000人易?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次罷工係全港人授權<br />\n唔係為自己，更為全港人發聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日成功，香港將會百花齊放，其他工會接力三罷，疫情盡可能受控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次失敗，我地不嬲想爭取既<br />\n醫生病人比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n護士病人比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n床位距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文書工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防感染控制個人防護裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咩都fight唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懇情大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">即時罷工</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>醫護同行，守護港人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1545:得4300罷左<br />\n其他人去哂邊呀?"},{"pid":"15e4c4d15d05008dfa31ce9b65c98c77bd8fe8de","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"8e40a308f1a519950dc6b9c35ea13bd15a523119","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"6e2adea8babe6df1c98dde6c26856841e44cca26","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"034baa6df06f6b401e15616b129cc16bf62d8a8d","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"529edd10002362efa85c346f0c52fdd84a41af1e","tid":1861572,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"9d3f6d0f52ed220b68e5a2303cafa01526654c73","tid":1861572,"uid":226858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29285e44c89d4365269197bf03b19bd47f3a9d45","tid":1861572,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3d827a3619ede22ccddf5bcf54e2cd3e9c0a233","tid":1861572,"uid":208308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}